sub_title: Entrepreneur & Innovator - Everything for Engineering || Changing the way we do Engineering
summary: Co-founder EveryEng & 1Vorteil, I believe diverse expertise in Engineering, extending beyond IT is the need of the hour. Changing global trends indicate the creation of large-scale opportunities across different fields of engineering as every nation now is working towards self-sufficiency be it in manufacturing, construction, or power generation. Both my ventures 1Vorteil & EveryEng stand testament to the increasing relevance of quality engineers today - helping them with the right platform to learn, explore and get the right projects based on their unique skill set and expertise, paving the way to the new form of work culture with a platform where an individual has the freedom to take up projects that truly interest him and equipping companies with the option to pick the right professional.
